subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Miguel Ángel Jiménez won the Hong Kong Open title by a stroke after the third-round leader, Robert Karlsson, double-bogeyed the final hole. Jiménez had an eagle and five birdies in a three-under-par 67 at Hong Kong Golf Club for a total of 15-under 265.
